  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q1_IS_HH_HEAD
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask you some personal information.</p><p>1. Before we begin, to confirm, are you the household head?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Respondent Profile. The respondent should be the main-decision maker of the household. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask you some personal information.</p><p>Bago tayo magsimula, upang makumpirma, kayo po ba ang pinuno ng sambahayan?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Respondent Profile. The respondent should be the main-decision maker of the household. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask you some personal information.</p><p>Bago kita mag-poon, para makumpirma: ika ba an pasyente?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Respondent Profile. The respondent should be the main-decision maker of the household. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask you some personal information.</p><p>Sa dili pa kita magsugod, aron makompirma, ikaw ba ang punoan sa panimalay?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Respondent Profile. The respondent should be the main-decision maker of the household. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask you some personal information.</p><p>Sa wala pa ta magsugod, ikaw ba ang ulo sa panimalay?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Respondent Profile. The respondent should be the main-decision maker of the household. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask you some personal information.</p><p>Ugsa kita magtikang, para la makasiguro, ikaw ba an ulo han panimalay?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Respondent Profile. The respondent should be the main-decision maker of the household. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.RESPONDENT_NAME
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>Name: (Last Name, First Name, MI, Extension)</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Pangalan: (Apelyido, Pangalan, Inisyal, Extension)</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Ngaran: (Apelyido, Ngaran, MI, Extension)</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Name: (Last Name, First Name, MI, Extension)</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ngalan: (Apelyido, Pangalan, MI, Extension)</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano it imo ngaran? (Apelyido, Syahan nga ngaran, Butnga, Dugang ha ngaran )</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q2_BIRTH_MONTH
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>2. In what month were you born?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Sa anong buwan at taon kayo ipinanganak?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>2. In what month were you born?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>2. In what month were you born?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsa nga buwan ug tuig ka gipanganak?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano nga bulan ngan tuig ka natawo?</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q2_BIRTH_YEAR
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>2. In what year were you born?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Sa anong buwan at taon kayo ipinanganak?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>2. In what year were you born?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsang bulana ug tuiga ka gipanganak?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>2. In what year were you born?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano nga bulan ngan tuig ka natawo?</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q2_1_AGE
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>2.1 Just to confirm, how old are you as of your last birthday (in years)?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Para makumpirma, ilang taon na kayo noong inyong huling kaarawan (sa taon)?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Pira an edad mo base sa huring kaarawan mo? (sa taon)</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Pila na ang imong edad base sa imong pinakaulahi nga birthday (sa tuig)?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Para ma-confirm lang, pila na imong edad base sa imong miaging birthday (sa tuig)?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Para la makumpirma, pira na an imo edad tikang han imo urhi nga kaadlawan (ha mga tuig)?</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q3_SEX
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>3. What is your sex at birth?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano po ang inyong kasarian noong ipinanganak?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Ano an saimong kasarian kan ika pinangaki?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsa ang imong sekso sa pagkatawo?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsa ang imong sex sa pagkahimugso?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano an imo sekso han imo pagkatawo?</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q4_LGBTQIA
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>4. Are you part of the LGBTQIA+ community? (e.g., gay, lesbian, bisexual, etc.). It is fine if you are not comfortable answering.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Kayo po ba ay kabilang sa komunidad ng LGBTQIA+? (halimbawa: gay, lesbian, bisexual, atbp.) Maaari pong hindi sagutin kung hindi kayo komportable.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Parte ka ba kan LGBTQIA+ na komunidad? (hal. bakla, tomboy, bi, buda maski ano pa)</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Kabahin ba ka sa LGBTQIA+ nga komunidad? (pananglitan: gay, lesbian, bisexual, ug uban pa). Okay ra kung dili ka komportable nga motubag.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Miyembro ba ka sa LGBTQIA+ community? (pananglitan: bayot, tomboy, bisexual, ug uban pa). Okay ra kung dili ka komportable motubag.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Kaapi ka ba han komunidad han LGBTQIA+? (pananglitan, bayot, tomboy, biseksuwal, ngan iba pa). Waray problema kun dire ka komportable bumaton</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
