  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q19_HH_SIZE_TOTAL
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>19. How many total individuals (including children) live in your house now?</p><p class="instruction">Please count yourself and all the people who usually live with you. Please include those who are not living here now but will be back within six months, BUT do not include OFWs.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ilang lahat (kasama ang mga bata) ang kasalukuyang nakatira sa bahay ninyo?</p><p class="instruction">Please count yourself and all the people who usually live with you. Please include those who are not living here now but will be back within six months, BUT do not include OFWs.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>19. How many total individuals (including children) live in your house now?</p><p class="instruction">Please count yourself and all the people who usually live with you. Please include those who are not living here now but will be back within six months, BUT do not include OFWs.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Pila mo kabuok (lakip ang mga bata) ang nagpuyo karon sa inyong balay?</p><p class="instruction">Please count yourself and all the people who usually live with you. Please include those who are not living here now but will be back within six months, BUT do not include OFWs.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Pila ka mga indibidwal (apil ang mga bata) ang nagpuyo karon sa inyong balay?</p><p class="instruction">Please count yourself and all the people who usually live with you. Please include those who are not living here now but will be back within six months, BUT do not include OFWs.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Pira kabug-usan nga indibidwal (upod na an kabataan) an naukoy yana ha iyo balay?</p><p class="instruction">Please count yourself and all the people who usually live with you. Please include those who are not living here now but will be back within six months, BUT do not include OFWs.</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q20_HH_CHILDREN
    conditions:
      - questionText:
