  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q30_NAME
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>We will now ask for some personal information about your household members.</p><p>30. Name (LAST NAME, FIRST NAME &amp; MIDDLE NAME, EXT)</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the characteristics of the Household. The respondent can answer on behalf of the household member. However, if the household member is present during the interview, they may provide their answers. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. For the enumerator: please check that the total number is equal to the number answered in Q19.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>We will now ask for some personal information about your household members.</p><p>PANGALAN</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the characteristics of the Household. The respondent can answer on behalf of the household member. However, if the household member is present during the interview, they may provide their answers. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. For the enumerator: please check that the total number is equal to the number answered in Q19.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>We will now ask for some personal information about your household members.</p><p>Pangaran (Apelyido, Pangaran, MI, Ext.)</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the characteristics of the Household. The respondent can answer on behalf of the household member. However, if the household member is present during the interview, they may provide their answers. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. For the enumerator: please check that the total number is equal to the number answered in Q19.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>We will now ask for some personal information about your household members.</p><p>Pangalan (APELYIDO, UNANG PANGALAN UG MIDDLE NAME, EXT)</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the characteristics of the Household. The respondent can answer on behalf of the household member. However, if the household member is present during the interview, they may provide their answers. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. For the enumerator: please check that the total number is equal to the number answered in Q19.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>We will now ask for some personal information about your household members.</p><p>Ngalan (Isulat ang kumpletong ngalan sa miyembro sa panimalay)</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the characteristics of the Household. The respondent can answer on behalf of the household member. However, if the household member is present during the interview, they may provide their answers. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. For the enumerator: please check that the total number is equal to the number answered in Q19.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>We will now ask for some personal information about your household members.</p><p>Ngaran (Isurat an kompleto nga ngaran hit HH nga miyembro)</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the characteristics of the Household. The respondent can answer on behalf of the household member. However, if the household member is present during the interview, they may provide their answers. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. For the enumerator: please check that the total number is equal to the number answered in Q19.</p>
