  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q35_HAS_DISABILITY
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>35. Do you identify as a person with a disability?</p><p class="instruction">If this is line 1 (the respondent): compare with their Section B disability answer Q7 — <b>~~getvaluelabel(Q7_IS_PWD)~~</b>.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Kinikilala ba ninyo ang sarili bilang isang taong may kapansanan?</p><p class="instruction">If this is line 1 (the respondent): compare with their Section B disability answer Q7 — <b>~~getvaluelabel(Q7_IS_PWD)~~</b>.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>May mental o pisikal ka bang kapansanan?</p><p class="instruction">If this is line 1 (the respondent): compare with their Section B disability answer Q7 — <b>~~getvaluelabel(Q7_IS_PWD)~~</b>.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Gi-ila ba nimo ang imong kaugalingon isip usa ka tawo nga adunay kapansanan?</p><p class="instruction">If this is line 1 (the respondent): compare with their Section B disability answer Q7 — <b>~~getvaluelabel(Q7_IS_PWD)~~</b>.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Nagpaila ba ka isip usa ka tawo nga adunay kapansanan/PWD?</p><p class="instruction">If this is line 1 (the respondent): compare with their Section B disability answer Q7 — <b>~~getvaluelabel(Q7_IS_PWD)~~</b>.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Nag-iidentify ka ba nga may kapansanan?</p><p class="instruction">If this is line 1 (the respondent): compare with their Section B disability answer Q7 — <b>~~getvaluelabel(Q7_IS_PWD)~~</b>.</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q36_SPECIFY_DISABILITY
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>36. Would you like to specify the type of disability?</p>
          FIL: |
