  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q38_DISABILITY_TYPE
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>38. Based on the presented PWD Identification Card, what type of disability is indicated?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Batay sa ipinakitang PWD Identification Card, anong uri ng kapansanan ang nakasaad?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Base sa tigpresenta na PWD ID Card, anong klase kan disability ang nakalaag?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Base sa gipakita nga PWD Identification Card, unsang klase sa kapansanan ang nakabutang?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Base sa gipakita nga PWD Identification Card, unsa nga klase sa kakulangan ang nakabutang?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Base han iginpresentar nga PWD Identification Card, ano nga klase hin kapansanan an iginpapakita?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
