  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q62_PURCHASE_FREQ
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to your access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for you and members of your household to purchase or receive medicines.</p><p>62. How often do you purchase or receive medicines?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Access to Medicines of the household. For this section, we will ask the respondent about how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to your access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for you and members of your household to purchase or receive medicines.</p><p>Gaano kadalas kang bumibili o tumatanggap ng mga gamot?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Access to Medicines of the household. For this section, we will ask the respondent about how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to your access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for you and members of your household to purchase or receive medicines.</p><p>Mga pirang beses ka magbakal o makaresibi ki bulong?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Access to Medicines of the household. For this section, we will ask the respondent about how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to your access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for you and members of your household to purchase or receive medicines.</p><p>Kapila kasagaran ka mupalit o mangayo ug tambal?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Access to Medicines of the household. For this section, we will ask the respondent about how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to your access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for you and members of your household to purchase or receive medicines.</p><p>Unsa ka sagad nimong gipalit o nadawat nga mga tambal?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Access to Medicines of the household. For this section, we will ask the respondent about how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to your access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for you and members of your household to purchase or receive medicines.</p><p>Mationan-o kaagsob kamo pumalit o kumarawat hin mga medisina?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Access to Medicines of the household. For this section, we will ask the respondent about how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q63_PRESCRIPTION_TYPE
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>63. Was the most recent medicine purchased prescribed by a doctor or over-the-counter (OTC) medicine (no need for a prescription)?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ang pinakahuling gamot na binili ba ay may reseta ng doktor o nabili ng hindi kailangan ang reseta over-the-counter (OTC)?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Ang pinaka recent na binakal na bulong tigprescribe saimo kan doctor o over-the-counter (OTC) na bulong (dai kaipuhan ki reseta)?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang pinakaulahing tambal nga inyong napalit, nireseta ba kini sa doktor o over-the-counter (OTC) nga tambal (walay reseta)?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang pinakaulahing tambal nga imong gipalit, gi-reseta ba kini sa doktor o over-the-counter (OTC) nga tambal (dili na kinahanglan og reseta)?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>An pinakabag-o ba nga medisina nga ginpalit ginreseta hin doktor o medisina nga waray reseta (diri kinahanglan hin reseta)?</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q64_MEDICATIONS_LIST
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>64. What are the medications that you or any member of your household usually take? (List all medicines taken for the health condition.)</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang mga gamot na karaniwang iniinom mo o ng sinumang miyembro ng inyong sambahayan? PAKITALA ANG LAHAT NG GAMOT NA ININOM PARA SA KONDISYON SA KALUSUGAN.</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Anong mga bulong o medisina an saimo o miembro kan pamilya na pirmi tigabakal asin tigainom?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsa nga mga tambal ang kasagarang imnon sa imo o sa imong miyembro sa panimalay?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsa ang mga tambal nga kasagaran nimong ginainom o sa bisan kinsa nga miyembro sa inyong panimalay?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano an mga medisina nga kasagaran niyo gin-inom o hin-o man nga miyembro han iyo panimalay?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
