  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q69_GAMOT_HEARD
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>We will now ask about your awareness of the GAMOT package, and the medicines you availed in a GAMOT pharmacy. We will also ask some questions about your views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>69. Have you heard of the Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) Package, which is part of PhilHealth's YAKAP/Konsulta or primary care benefit package?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for awareness of the GAMOT package and generic and branded medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. Q69 to Q74, Q76 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>We will now ask about your awareness of the GAMOT package, and the medicines you availed in a GAMOT pharmacy. We will also ask some questions about your views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>Narinig na ba ninyo ang Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) Package, na bahagi ng PhilHealth YAKAP/Konsulta o primary care benefit package?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for awareness of the GAMOT package and generic and branded medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. Q69 to Q74, Q76 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>We will now ask about your awareness of the GAMOT package, and the medicines you availed in a GAMOT pharmacy. We will also ask some questions about your views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>Nadangog mo na an Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) package, na parte kan Philhealth's YAKAP/Konsulta o primary care benefit package?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for awareness of the GAMOT package and generic and branded medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. Q69 to Q74, Q76 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>We will now ask about your awareness of the GAMOT package, and the medicines you availed in a GAMOT pharmacy. We will also ask some questions about your views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>Nakadungog na ba ka bahin sa Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) Package, nga kabahin sa PhilHealth’s YAKAP/Konsulta o primary care benefit package?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for awareness of the GAMOT package and generic and branded medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. Q69 to Q74, Q76 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>We will now ask about your awareness of the GAMOT package, and the medicines you availed in a GAMOT pharmacy. We will also ask some questions about your views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>Nakadungog na ba ka bahin sa Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) Package, nga parte sa YAKAP/Konsulta o primary care benefit package sa PhilHealth?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for awareness of the GAMOT package and generic and branded medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. Q69 to Q74, Q76 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>We will now ask about your awareness of the GAMOT package, and the medicines you availed in a GAMOT pharmacy. We will also ask some questions about your views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>Nakabati ka na ba han Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) Package, nga parte han kanan PhilHealth YAKAP/Konsulta o primaryo nga mga benepisyo ha pag-antam nga package?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for awareness of the GAMOT package and generic and branded medicines. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. Q69 to Q74, Q76 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
