  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q72_GAMOT_OBTAINED
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>72. Did you get the medicines from the GAMOT Package during the past 6 months?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT facility.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Nakakuha ba kayo ng mga gamot mula sa GAMOT Package sa nakalipas na 6 na buwan?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT facility.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Nakakuha kaba kan mga medisina hali sa GAMOT Package kan nakaagi 6 anom na bulan?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT facility.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Nakakuha ba ka og tambal gikan sa GAMOT Package sulod sa milabay nga 6 ka bulan?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT facility.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Nakadawat ba ka og mga tambal gikan sa GAMOT Package niini nga miaging 6 ka bulan?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT facility.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Nakuha mo ba an mga medisina tikang han GAMOT Package han naglabay nga 6 ka bulan?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT facility.</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q73_GAMOT_MEDS_LIST
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>73. What are the medications that you obtained from the GAMOT Package? [LIST]</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano-ano ang mga gamot na nakuha mo mula sa GAMOT Package? LISTA</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Anong mga bulong an saimong nakua hali sa GAMOT Package?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsa nga mga tambal ang imong nakuha gikan sa GAMOT Package? [I-LISTA]</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsa ang mga tambal nga imong nadawat gikan sa GAMOT Package? [ILISTA]</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano an mga medisina nga iyo nakuha tikang han GAMOT Package? [LISTA]</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
