          EN: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related your PhilHealth registration experience. We will also confirm your PhilHealth registration status and membership.</p><p>79. How did you find out about how to register to PhilHealth?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for PhilHealth registration experience and registration status and membership. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related your PhilHealth registration experience. We will also confirm your PhilHealth registration status and membership.</p><p>Paano po ninyo nalaman kung paano magparehistro sa PhilHealth?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for PhilHealth registration experience and registration status and membership. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related your PhilHealth registration experience. We will also confirm your PhilHealth registration status and membership.</p><p>Pano mo naaraman kun pano magrehistro sa PhilHealth?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for PhilHealth registration experience and registration status and membership. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related your PhilHealth registration experience. We will also confirm your PhilHealth registration status and membership.</p><p>Giunsa nimo pagkahibalo kung unsaon pagparehistro sa PhilHealth?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for PhilHealth registration experience and registration status and membership. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related your PhilHealth registration experience. We will also confirm your PhilHealth registration status and membership.</p><p>Giunsa nimo paghibalo kung unsaon pagparehistro sa PhilHealth?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for PhilHealth registration experience and registration status and membership. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          WAR: |
