  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q89_HAS_USUAL_FACILITY
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>We will now ask questions about your access to a primary care provider.</p><p>89. In the past 12 months, do you have a clinic, or health center that you usually go to?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for Access to a primary care provider. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>We will now ask questions about your access to a primary care provider.</p><p>Sa nakalipas na 12 buwan, mayroon ka bang klinika o health center na madalas mong pinupuntahan? Ano ang pangalan ng pasilidad?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for Access to a primary care provider. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>We will now ask questions about your access to a primary care provider.</p><p>Sa nakaaging 12 bulan, may aram ka na clinic, o health center na pirmi mo pigdudumanan? Ano an ngaran kan pasilidad?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for Access to a primary care provider. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>We will now ask questions about your access to a primary care provider.</p><p>Sa milabay nga 12 ka bulan, aduna ba kay klinika o health center nga kasagarang adtoan? Unsa ang ngalan sa pasilidad?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for Access to a primary care provider. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>We will now ask questions about your access to a primary care provider.</p><p>Sa miaging 12 ka bulan, aduna ba kang klinika o health center nga kasagaran nimong adtoan? Unsa ang pangalan sa pasilidad?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for Access to a primary care provider. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>We will now ask questions about your access to a primary care provider.</p><p>Han naglabay nga 12 ka bulan, mayda ka ba klinika, o health center nga kasagaran mo kadtuan? Ano an ngaran han pasilidad?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for Access to a primary care provider. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q89_1_FACILITY_NAME
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>89.1. What is the name of the facility?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang pangalan ng pasilidad?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Anong ngaran kan pasilidad?</p>
