  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q108_REFERRED
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>We will be asking about your experiences and satisfaction on referrals.</p><p>108. In the past 6 months, did a healthcare worker refer you to another facility or specialist for further care or specialized care?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Experiences and Satisfaction with Referrals. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>We will be asking about your experiences and satisfaction on referrals.</p><p>Sa nakalipas na anim na buwan, ikaw ba ay nirefer ng isang health care worker sa ibang pasilidad o espesyalista para sa karagdagang o espesyalisadong pangangalaga?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Experiences and Satisfaction with Referrals. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>We will be asking about your experiences and satisfaction on referrals.</p><p>Sa nakaaging 6 anom na bulan, may nagrefer ba saimo na healthcare worker sa ibang pasilidad o especialista para sa specialized care?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Experiences and Satisfaction with Referrals. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>We will be asking about your experiences and satisfaction on referrals.</p><p>Sa milabay nga 6 ka bulan, adunay ba healthcare worker nga nag-refer nimo ngadto sa lain nga pasilidad o espesyalista alang sa dugang o espesyal nga pag-atiman?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Experiences and Satisfaction with Referrals. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>We will be asking about your experiences and satisfaction on referrals.</p><p>Sa miaging 6 ka bulan, gi-refer ka ba sa usa ka healthcare worker ngadto sa laing pasilidad o espesyalista para sa dugang nga pag-atiman o espesyal nga pag-atiman?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Experiences and Satisfaction with Referrals. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>We will be asking about your experiences and satisfaction on referrals.</p><p>Han naglabay nga 6 ka bulan, mayda ba na trabaho ha healthcare nga nagrefer ha imo ha iba nga pasilidad o espesyalista para hin dugang nga pag-ataman o espesyalista nga pag-ataman?</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Experiences and Satisfaction with Referrals. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p>
